#rhn_register ( it will ask for username/passwd) and we will get new repo in local system
Yum update ( it will update all package)
Yum repolist(to see repo in local system
Yum check-update( to check how many package to be updated)
Yum updateinfo summary
Yum updateinfo –security
Yum update –security ( to install only security package)
Yum clean all
Reboot
#######Rollback
Yum history   ( to see what package installed which need to be rollback)
Yum history undo 7 ( 7 is the id)
